query:
SELECT 
  p.name,
  COALESCE(SUM(te.durationHours), 0) / 100 as userHours,
  COALESCE(upq.quotaHours, p.totalQuotaHours) as userQuota,
  (COALESCE(SUM(te.durationHours), 0) / 100) / COALESCE(upq.quotaHours, p.totalQuotaHours) * 100 as percentage
FROM projects p
LEFT JOIN timeEntries te ON te.projectId = p.id AND te.userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE openId LIKE '%vikram%' LIMIT 1)
LEFT JOIN userProjectQuotas upq ON upq.projectId = p.id AND upq.userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE openId LIKE '%vikram%' LIMIT 1)
WHERE p.status = 'active'
GROUP BY p.id, p.name, p.totalQuotaHours, upq.quotaHours
ORDER BY percentage DESC;
